    <mxCell id="20" value="✅ Pros:&#xa;• Simple — fewer moving parts&#xa;• Fast direct pipeline&#xa;• No bot/Teams registration needed&#xa;&#xa;❌ Cons:&#xa;• No user review before posting&#xa;• Webhook only — 0 fallback&#xa;• No retry if pipeline fails&#xa;• State lost on restart&#xa;• Single user, single board&#xa;• Cannot queue concurrent meetings" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#d6b656;fillColor=#fff2cc;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=1;fontSize=11;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=6;" vertex="1" parent="1">
