    <mxCell id="70" value="✅ Pros:&#xa;• User reviews insights before Monday post&#xa;• Poll fallback: 0 missed meetings ✅&#xa;• Service Bus: retry ×10 + dead-letter queue&#xa;• Table Storage: state survives restarts/scale&#xa;• Concurrent meetings handled via queue&#xa;• Regenerate insights if not satisfied&#xa;• Fully serverless — ~$0.01/month&#xa;• Application Insights: full observability&#xa;&#xa;❌ Cons:&#xa;• Graph webhook not yet firing reliably&#xa;• Single organizer only (MULTI_USER_ROUTING.md)&#xa;• 5 min max delay when using poll fallback" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fillColor=#dae8fc;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=1;fontSize=11;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=6;" vertex="1" parent="1">
